<h2>How We Test</h2>
<p>Each AI data and analytics tool was evaluated on: accuracy of results, ease of use, feature set, integration capabilities, data visualization quality, response time, and overall value. Tests included real-world scenarios like conducting research with cited sources, extracting data from complex websites, building unified dashboards across business platforms, and performing ad-hoc data analysis on spreadsheets.</p>
